00:47:08.870 --> 00:47:11.820
So if you're doing something
on Bank of America,

00:47:11.820 --> 00:47:14.390
Bank of America might
then give you points

00:47:14.390 --> 00:47:16.010
and share generously.

00:47:16.010 --> 00:47:18.560
And a lot of the bank
programs will share maybe up

00:47:18.560 --> 00:47:20.060
