00:47:48.620 --> 00:47:50.960
This is the US model.

00:47:50.960 --> 00:47:54.450
It does not cost
this much in India.

00:47:54.450 --> 00:47:57.700
It does not cost
this much in China.

00:47:57.700 --> 00:47:59.460
So in many other
countries the jump

00:47:59.460 --> 00:48:03.270
