card payment systems.

00:48:03.270 --> 00:48:04.510
It costs a lot less.

00:48:04.510 --> 00:48:06.720
But in the US,
our payment system

00:48:06.720 --> 00:48:10.440
is significantly built
on credit card rails--

00:48:10.440 --> 00:48:15.750
rails like tracks-- it's called.

00:48:15.750 --> 00:48:16.455
So cross-border.

00:48:16.455 --> 00:48:18.330
I'm not going to go
