Right.

00:48:34.040 --> 00:48:36.540
GARY GENSLER: So Shimon's point
is that we, in this country,

00:48:36.540 --> 00:48:39.450
have bundled the credit
provision with the payment

00:48:39.450 --> 00:48:40.770
provision.

00:48:40.770 --> 00:48:45.450
And there are many of us that
when the merchant says, give me

00:48:45.450 --> 00:48:47.700
