00:49:05.580 --> 00:49:10.560
along in our country, we had
established credit card payment

00:49:10.560 --> 00:49:11.970
rails.

00:49:11.970 --> 00:49:14.130
And most of the internet
payments, whether it

00:49:14.130 --> 00:49:16.830
was for your mortgage--

00:49:16.830 --> 00:49:18.690
well, usually not
mortgage, but whether it

00:49:18.690 --> 00:49:23.820
was for your utilities or
your small dollar payments

00:49:23.820 --> 00:49:26.250
were built on top of
the credit card rails.

00:49:26.250 --> 00:49:29.370
Your mortgage-- most mortgage
lenders would say, no.

00:49:29.370 --> 00:49:32.850
I don't want to pay the 2.7%.

00:49:36.490 --> 00:49:38.290
We didn't have
enough market power

00:49:38.290 --> 00:49:40.060
