campaign to get

00:49:40.060 --> 00:49:42.790
people to give it
to us in checks,

00:49:42.790 --> 00:49:46.780
or to Zelle payment to us.

00:49:46.780 --> 00:49:49.540
But this 2.7 is economic rents.

00:49:49.540 --> 00:49:52.540
This is a form of
economic rents.

00:49:52.540 --> 00:49:53.050
Fraud.

00:49:53.050 --> 00:49:56.905
