00:50:05.060 --> 00:50:10.150
So of this 270 basis
points-- or 2.7%--

00:50:10.150 --> 00:50:13.460
less than 10% of it's really
going to pay for fraud.

00:50:13.460 --> 00:50:17.000
Now fraud is a really big
