00:51:02.980 --> 00:51:03.480
Right?

00:51:03.480 --> 00:51:05.230
When you're using
money you already have.

00:51:05.230 --> 00:51:07.850
Well, that credit risk is much,
much smaller than the money

00:51:07.850 --> 00:51:10.210
that you're not going to
pay me back if [INAUDIBLE]..

00:51:10.210 --> 00:51:14.350
So I would say the big thing
that I would encourage everyone

00:51:14.350 --> 00:51:15.730
is to separate the two.

00:51:15.730 --> 00:51:18.550
And more to the point of
a what is the credit risk.

00:51:22.138 --> 00:51:23.680
I would say it's
probably [? half. ?]

00:51:23.680 --> 00:51:25.388
GARY GENSLER: So I
don't know the number,

00:51:25.388 --> 00:51:26.500
