00:51:26.500 --> 00:51:31.960
But I would caution to say
the compensation for credit

00:51:31.960 --> 00:51:33.520
doesn't only come out of this.

00:51:33.520 --> 00:51:35.860
It also comes out
of the anywhere

00:51:35.860 --> 00:51:39.610
from 18% to 27% interest
rates they're charging.

00:51:39.610 --> 00:51:47.100
So when you think about it
like, it's a dual model.

00:51:47.100 --> 00:51:51.280
It's this, which is not
