00:51:55.330 --> 00:51:57.820
as a payment rail.

00:51:57.820 --> 00:52:00.400
And then you charge an
interest rate spread,

00:52:00.400 --> 00:52:04.390
which is over 1,000
basis points, usually.

00:52:04.390 --> 00:52:08.540
The spread versus
underlying bank borrowing

00:52:08.540 --> 00:52:12.360
tends to be anywhere from
1,000 to 1,800 basis points

00:52:12.360 --> 00:52:14.480
on some of these.

00:52:14.480 --> 00:52:17.270
But I'm not saying
it's separate.

00:52:17.270 --> 00:52:18.860
It's two business models.

00:52:18.860 --> 00:52:20.630
Let me churn on.

00:52:20.630 --> 00:52:23.330
AUDIENCE: I'm just going to
