00:58:28.920 --> 00:58:32.460
have to figure out how to get
your cost structure down there.

00:58:32.460 --> 00:58:34.710
Or is it for the
multi-million dollar treasury

00:58:34.710 --> 00:58:38.520
function, for the
Fortune 500 or the World

00:58:38.520 --> 00:58:41.790
1,000 or whatever
treasury function,

00:58:41.790 --> 00:58:43.860
where they're really
talking about frictions

00:58:43.860 --> 00:58:46.480
which are in basis points.

00:58:46.480 --> 00:58:50.740
But still, the bridge currency--
crypto bridge currencies--

00:58:50.740 --> 00:58:54.640
