00:58:57.460 --> 00:59:00.820
to the retail remittance side.

00:59:00.820 --> 00:59:03.012
The percentage
fees are different.

00:59:03.012 --> 00:59:05.470
And you just have to be able
to say, well, can I get inside

00:59:05.470 --> 00:59:07.900
